name: Young Zelda (OoT)
description:
The next Zelda LoRA (only 4 more and a fan outfit to go.... so much Zelda). See the bottom for Zelda choices. Requested ones will come sooner.

Quirks:
3/31 images were portraits so I highly suggest you toss 'portrait' in the negatives unless you really want one
You will also likely want to prompt 'looking at viewer' unless you want her staring listlessly off to the side

As Usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.8

Next Zelda:
Shiek (by request)

Options for after that:
Toon Zelda
Tetra
Skyward Sword Zelda
Gashi-gashi outfit (no shot this works hahaha)
